          <span class="word-translate">weil<span class="translation">because</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">sie<span class="translation">it</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">eine<span class="translation">a</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">ähnliche<span class="translation">similar</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">Wirkung<span class="translation">effect</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">wie<span class="translation">like</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">Medizin<span class="translation">medicine</span></span>
          <span class="word-translate">hat<span class="translation">has</span></span>.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mt-8"><strong>Hinweis:</strong> Bewegen Sie den Mauszeiger über ein Wort, um seine Übersetzung zu sehen.</p>
